l bilirubin elevation greater than 2 times ULN, aminotransferase elevations are greater than 8 times ULN, or aminotransferase elevations persist beyond 2 weeks.', 'Synergism', 'The use of bedaquiline with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/137497/', '', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Nelarabine, Fludarabine, Decitabine, Azacitidine, Capecitabine, Theophylline, More', 'Capreomycin, Pyrazinamide, Rifamycin, Sulfamethoxazole, Rifapentine, Streptomycin, Rifampicin, Cycloserine, Rifabutin, Isoniazid, Ethambutol, More', 1767369485);
